metadata.name: CBDC Airdrop
metadata.description:
"They're coming. The angels are coming for you.  
But listen, your life could depend on this.  
Don't blink.  
Don't even blink. Blink and you're dead.  
They are fast. Faster than you can believe. Don't turn your back, don't look away, and don't blink.  
Good luck."

----

the sale of the NFT includes the transfer of the author's representation rights. Meaning the owner can publicly display the NFT as they see fit.
